Kirsty smiled as she posed on the side of a dreamy-looking swimming pool, with a verdant, rural backdrop visible behind her. The presenter showed off her toned physique in a plunging triangle bikini featuring a black and white striped pattern. The star was looking incredibly tanned and completed her summery look with a large pair of sunglasses and put her long dark hair in a ponytail. She captioned the photo: “Last dip before home! The best week with family and friends, always sad to leave.” (sic)   